<p>Hi <%= @user.name.presence || @user.username %>,</p>

<p>Someone requested a password reset for your BBC Farsi admin account
(<%= @user.username %>). Click the link below to choose a new password:</p>

<p><%= link_to "Reset your password", edit_admin_password_reset_url(token: @token) %></p>

<p>This link expires in 20 minutes. If you didn't request this, you can
safely ignore this email — your password won't be changed.</p>
